# ^^^ LINE 1 IS THE ONLY THING THAT MATTERS. atlas-fetch.sh reads the first line of
#     ~/.claude/atlas-source and ignores the rest.
#
# Copy this file to `~/.claude/atlas-source` and set line 1 to ONE source:
#   - the official site:   https://atlas.paranoid.software   (recommended)
#   - a local clone:       /Users/you/Code/paranoid-software/atlas
#   - a local dev server:  http://localhost:8088
#
# It's mutually exclusive — a URL (http/https → curl) OR a path (→ cat). One line. Done.
